If ever there was a time for Britain to lead by example on climate change, it is right now.

By the way, what we want (and need!) in the long term is a sensible immigration law (that has nothing to do with asylum).

== EUROPEE DOMENICA 26 MAGGIO: ECCO COME SI VOTA! ==

Si vota SOLO domenica 26 MAGGIO, dalle 7 alle 23, barrando il simbolo LEGA. Nelle righe affianco al simbolo puoi esprimere fino a 3 preferenze (se più di una, includi sia un uomo che una donna).

== EUROPEAN SUNDAY 26 MAY: HERE'S HOW TO VOTE! ==

You can vote ONLY on Sunday 26 MAY, from 7am to 11pm, by crossing the LEGA symbol. In the lines next to the symbol you can express up to 3 preferences (if more than one, include both a man and a woman).
#primalitalia #26maggiovotoLega https://twitter.com/LegaSalvini/status/1126813915747442688/photo/1

text:
A to i na úrovni EPP. Apelujeme na urychlené přijetí Ukrajiny mezi kandidátské země pro vstup do EU.

Předsednictvo KDU-ČSL zároveň konstatuje, že Rusko tím, že vystavuje bombardování civilní obyvatelstvo, páchá válečné zločiny v podobě zasahování civilních cílů.
party_name: Křesťanská a demokratická unie – Československá strana lidová
translation:
And even at the EPP level. We appeal for the accelerated acceptance of Ukraine among the candidate countries for joining the EU.

At the same time, the Presidium of the KDU-ČSL notes that Russia, by exposing the civilian population to bombing, is committing war crimes in the form of targeting civilian targets.
